{"text": "It is possible to sleep several consecutive nights in a snow cave, but care must be taken since a slight ice crust may develop on the inside of the cave from moisture in the exhaled air of the inhabitants. This is thought to result in reduced air ventilation through the snow cave walls and roof, and thus increase the risk of suffocation. As a precaution, it is common to scrape off a thin layer from the inside of the cave ceiling each night spent in the cave.", "embedding": [0.016851386, 0.06411562, -0.19283396, 0.035346735, 0.011430557, 0.024828184, -0.0059215943, 0.02794622, 0.0064814975, -0.06817866, -0.03631679, -0.001752644, 0.05358842, 0.057441186, -0.05817416, -0.020662809, 0.041216195, -0.027320785, 0.05602944, -0.0149844615, -0.07660787, -0.0029527775, 0.02419338, -0.01172619, -0.018265178, 0.06388458, 0.101179786, 0.049893938, -0.026069457, 0.052206103, 0.07364032, -0.017810779, -0.012238174, -0.035786923, -0.019685656, -0.08247312, 0.037335422, 0.017361548, 0.029527294, -0.011050704, 0.042329583, -0.004360522, 0.037684254, -0.03329813, 0.03146677, -0.02035004, 0.042157967, -0.02964321, 0.04126727, -0.034592483, 0.08331063, -0.07505727, -0.018659374, -0.037874207, 0.022686379, -0.004845866, 0.02717206, -0.04116579, 0.07143075, -0.03913848, 0.056575406, 0.021439867, -0.015496403, -9.844337e-05, 0.016847264, 0.004361099, -0.044057257, 0.028151527, 0.024952885, -0.000903023, 0.060869798, 0.014328209, -0.011544547, 0.016125381, -0.05455795, 0.022969104, -0.023096204, 0.055076562, -0.0038353535, 0.069603205, 0.046239413, 0.0028378095, 0.036606207, -0.013462528, 0.034476556, 0.028936861, -0.0048932214, -0.011724863, -0.010318396, 0.088033415, -0.030838719, 0.0069968123, 0.024159877, 0.06790959, -0.07812187, 0.034368087, 0.047812417, 0.0804523, -0.07543394, 0.018264547, -0.035620145, -0.04914246, 0.003512122, 0.040014, 0.018268654, 0.019686118, -0.04687202, 0.024819812, 0.0011574767, 0.032279868, -0.062492155, 0.06521537, -0.020474583, 0.00913495, 0.0555